revision.text:
'''Sarutahiko-no-Oh-Kami''' is a [[kami]], a deity of the [[Japan|Japanese]] religion of [[Shinto]].

Sarutahiko is credited as being the guardian of the earth, and appears in the [[Kojiki]] as the kami who guided [[Amaterasu]]'s grandchild from heaven to earth. He is the main deity of [[Tsubaki Jinja]], one of the oldest [[Jinja (Shinto)|shrine]]s in Japan.

{{japan-stub}}
{{religion-stub}}

[[Category:shinto kami]]

